{"tid":936098,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本電視台踢爆攜程Trip.com呃鳩人","createTime":"2018-12-10T13:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T12:48:36.000Z","uid":1251,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"03cd5d7a984719f84ff004c29cb1846f208f455b","tid":936098,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:36:28.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒爆由中國OTA（Online Travel Agency）「攜程網」<a href=\"http://經營的網站Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%93%E7%87%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Trip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=111b27a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">經營的網站Trip.com</a>出現「假訂房」情況，有受害者經網站訂房及支付房間費用後發現旅館其實並沒有收到預約。<br />\n<br />\n據日本放送協會NHK報道，熱海一間溫泉旅館收到客人來電確認元旦的訂房及用餐，<a href=\"http://該名客人經Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A9%B2%E5%90%8D%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E7%B6%93Trip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=2d33562e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">該名客人經Trip.com</a>訂房，但旅館方面卻查找不到該名客人的預約資料，<a href=\"http://調查後發現Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%BE%8C%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BETrip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=0d3c4060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">調查後發現Trip.com</a>上的住宿方案其實旅館並未提供，而且旅館的元旦房間早在一個月前已額滿。<br />\n<br />\n日本觀光廳已進行調查，發現站內這種「假訂房」的情況達400件。通常這種「假訂房」的情況都是「預訂無法取消」而且房價比一般貴2倍以上。日本多間酒店旅館在除夕元旦的訂房早已爆滿，<a href=\"http://唯獨Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%94%AF%E7%8D%A8Trip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=3ff1823a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">唯獨Trip.com</a>仍然有空房可以預訂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://事發後Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%BE%8CTrip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=1eec79d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">事發後Trip.com</a>發出聲明，已停止與不良業者交易。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果查明預約屬於「假訂房」的話，將會全數退還房費給顧客。<br />\n<br />\n除了NHK外，日本旅行媒體Traicy亦有報道相關事件，<a href=\"http://並發現Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%A6%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BETrip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=2ea63612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">並發現Trip.com</a>的「假訂房」手法：這些預訂無法取消，而且通常標示「只剩最後一間」吸引客人預訂。<a href=\"http://客人預訂後Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E5%BE%8CTrip.com&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=fef493a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">客人預訂後Trip.com</a>發電郵表示「正等待酒店方面的確認」，而事實上根本沒有向酒店預約，並在等待客人臨時取消預約以收取退訂的手續費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/25722/?utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F25722%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_source%3Dclipboard_share&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=925d3da3\" target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/25722/?utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share</a>"},{"pid":"34ae2adf75562fa368abafea5d09846df4779968","tid":936098,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c98ca38d65ff7c90436a9713c21b87509a5ef4","tid":936098,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:42:07.000Z","msg":"支那嘢不意外"},{"pid":"ecd3f88a977547b426492fa6fb8166cf5303f0cd","tid":936098,"uid":14591,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"訂左之後就靠自己keep住check啦，佢個客服未至於去到冇人聽，有問題打上去都有人幫到手既。不過訂之前最好緊係上hotelscombined睇，見到個個都冇房得佢有就肯定有蠱惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279ca5779e35327962abfed